{"tid":1531801,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"唔好覺得法庭會偏幫示威者","createTime":"2019-09-02T10:38:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T11:08:10.000Z","uid":160964,"like":12,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"fe92fb57c3fcf3f1da09d85212799eb7e0df38a8","tid":1531801,"uid":160964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T10:38:37.000Z","msg":"事實上法例係維護政權，律政司亂告先會告唔入<br />\n你地宜家做d反政府示威，正常係一定入罪"},{"pid":"69fe3bacb5d50b35fc8a7833316e30a10951dd9e","tid":1531801,"uid":69525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T10:39:25.000Z","msg":"[置頂] 建議9月8日百萬人大遊行/集會，請求美國國會通過人權及民主法案<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1530650\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1530650</a><br />\n<br />\n901 機場測試係成功<br />\n辛苦曬行左20公里既手足 勿被帶風向<br />\n<br />\n908 我希望美國巴絲手足都有遊行<br />\n聲援香港同埋同要請求美國國會通過人權法!<br />\n<br />\n908 建議：<br />\n大量英文文宣/紙牌<br />\n高舉大量美國議員大頭相<br />\n(睇下邊個出過聲又重要既)<br />\n高舉大量國旗<br />\n唔建議勇武，因為主題涉及美國<br />\n(另一原因係 廢時佢又區區有狗搜身兼<br />\n補充文具需時又珍貴)<br />\n領事館門前唱國歌<br />\n無人申請不反 都要照上街<br />\n<br />\n需要文宣制圖 然後我幫你宣傳<br />\n由今日開始宣! 908照上街!<br />\n<br />\n建議內容copy某位巴打既<br />\n9月我要照上街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6df7f3eacd4136660524760c5a5eb7d773b318c","tid":1531801,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T10:40:10.000Z","msg":"(LIHKG please set up an English Platform for us) <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"> US Congress will be resumed on 9/9!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/no